{"tid":1513764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★睇好？】佐敦迷你地舖，面積19方呎，開價108萬元 勝在近港鐵站","createTime":"2019-08-28T13:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T13:03:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3149156b9a1b1ee2fa5231ebfc5bcebbdad763d6","tid":1513764,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"「你可能會聽過有十幾呎嘅商場劏舖，但十幾呎超納米街舖，就聞所未聞」。佐敦文蔚樓一個迷你地舖，實用面積僅約19方呎，將透過環亞拍賣於下月初推出，連租約開價108萬元，呎價56,842元。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該舖現作儲物用途，位於文成街，兩旁均為食肆，現時月租3,700元，以開價計算，租金回報約4.1厘。資料顯示，該舖去年成交價約135萬元，現拍賣開價較其低達27萬元或兩成。<br />\n<br />\n文蔚樓與另外七幢同樣以文字開頭的大廈，被稱為「八文樓」，於六十年代落成。物業雖然樓齡較高，但勝在地理位置佳，只需數分鐘步程，直達港鐵柯士甸站及西九龍高鐵站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190828/bkn-20190828183827508-0828_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190828%2Fbkn-20190828183827508-0828_00842_001.html&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5LXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=3b2dac94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190828/bkn-20190828183827508-0828_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fd2b847ca614ee64d62bce851df7ac951d916543","tid":1513764,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:03:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士進程請入，一個也不能少不是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c5c33caa16bdc461d0577cb70cb48855cb97da6a","tid":1513764,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=1